<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Volleyball AI Analysis</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        /* Custom Gradient Animation */
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #60a5fa, #c084fc);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        body {
            background-color: #0f172a; /* Dark Slate Background */
            color: #e2e8f0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="font-sans antialiased">

    <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 bg-slate-900/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-slate-800">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between h-16">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-xl font-bold gradient-text">VolleyVision AI</span>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden md:block">
                    <div class="ml-10 flex items-baseline space-x-4">
                        <a href="#demo" class="hover:text-blue-400 px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium">Demo</a>
                        <a href="#features" class="hover:text-blue-400 px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium">Features</a>
                        <a href="https://github.com/itsYoga" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition">GitHub</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="relative pt-32 pb-12 sm:pt-40 sm:pb-16">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
                <span class="block">Volleyball Performance</span>
                <span class="block gradient-text">Analysis System</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-3 max-w-md mx-auto text-base text-slate-400 sm:text-lg md:mt-5 md:text-xl md:max-w-3xl">
                Leveraging Computer Vision and Deep Learning to track ball trajectory, analyze kill rates, and optimize team strategy.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-10 max-w-sm mx-auto sm:max-w-none sm:flex sm:justify-center">
                <a href="#demo" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10 transition">
                    View Analysis
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="demo" class="py-12 bg-slate-900">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="lg:text-center mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-base text-blue-400 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">System Demo</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 text-3xl leading-8 font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
                    AI in Action
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-slate-700 bg-slate-800 aspect-video flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="text-center p-8">
                    <svg class="mx-auto h-12 w-12 text-slate-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z" />
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-slate-400">System Demo Video / Analysis Dashboard</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">(Upload media to repo to display here)</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="features" class="py-16 bg-slate-800/50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="lg:text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-base text-blue-400 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">Capabilities</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 text-3xl leading-8 font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
                    Advanced Metrics
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
                <div class="bg-slate-900 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-500 transition">
                    <h3 class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-white">Ball Trajectory Tracking</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-base text-slate-400">
                        Real-time tracking of the volleyball's path using computer vision to analyze set accuracy and serve curves.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-500 transition">
                    <h3 class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-white">Kill Rate Analysis</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-base text-slate-400">
                        Automated calculation of spike effectiveness and kill rates compared to commercial baselines.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-500 transition">
                    <h3 class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-white">Tactical Heatmaps</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-base text-slate-400">
                        Visualizing player positioning and attack zones to identify defensive gaps.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-800">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-8 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-base text-slate-500">
                &copy; 2025 YuJia Liang. Hosted on GitHub Pages.
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
